messages.text: No, nose fine. And SHE was there
Your cat? BTW what kind of name is that
Her previous owner said that’s what she was called
Yeah. Listen I think she’s evil … She just stared at me, motionless
All cats look like evil masterminds, nothing new there
I think she was the one who hurt me
I think I saw her jump off the bed just as I woke up
Maybe she wanted you to feed her
No, there’s something creepy going on here …
I’ve been feeling really faint and dizzy
You’re just learning how to be a cat person
Do you know what the difference between cats and dogs is?
A dog thinks: these people feed me, take care of me and give me gifts
Can you stop with the jokes
A cat thinks: these people feed me, take care of me and give me gifts
There for I must be GOD
Ok sort of funny. Maybe she IS a god
And I’m about to taste her revenge
She’s held a grudge against me ever since I gave her litter away
And last night I woke up and my neck hurt
What has that got to do with anything
I went to get some water from the fridge and there she was
And her eyes glowed in the dark
Again, that’s what is supposed to happen
Well yeah, except … they were glowing RED …
You must have been have asleep still
What if she’s trying to hurt me back. Or Kill me?
Jeez Jenna. All in your head
Just make yourself a nice veggie smoothie and put on some ambient music when you go to bed
Who? What are you taking about?
Ah not this again! I need to sleep
I woke up in the middle of the night
And something hissed and bit me
And my hand, where she bit me
Is this some sort of nightmare you’re having?
And her eyes have turned red
Well get out of there then!
Now my other hand is all bloody as well
Akasha was the main Vampire Mother …
Or turn me into a weird cat vampire
Why hasn’t she killed you yet?
THANKS that’s so nice of you
No I mean, she could have, clearly
But she was keeping you ALIVE … And she’s letting you use your phone
What? There’s blood everywhere on me, hurry up!!
There were only two really, and I heard that one died
Does she know what we’re talking about?
I don’t know, she’s REALLY CLOSE NOW
HOLD ON I’ll go get her kitten
She’s BIT me again, she’s getting impatient
I’m about to faint, I’m freaking out
Not sure how I managed to convince Jack, but he gave it to me
He thinks I’m crazy for sure
Let it in through the cat door!
She’s licking him, no more red eyes
Open the door so we can clean you up!
How is everything? You looked very pale today
Yeah well, I have two cats to feed now…
